e></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 30, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104wmy1719769435039.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wmy1719769435039.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/wmy1719769435039.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ydm1665702627365\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $curline\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ydm1665702627365___curline_256999\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the line on which the cursor is positioned in the current Unifield.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ydm1665702627365__topic_d81524e1_d81525e1_d81526e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ydm1665702627365__p_d81527e1_d81528e1_d81529e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curline</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ydm1665702627365__topic_d53752e1_d53753e1_d53754e1_d53755e1_d53756e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d820828e66\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ydm1665702627365__p_d81533e1_d81534e1_d81535e1\">Line number where the cursor is currently positioned in the Uniface field editor.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ydm1665702627365__topic_d53757e1_d53758e1_d53759e1_d53760e1_d53761e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d820828e75\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ydm1665702627365__d6469e20\">Use in Form components, but only applicable to Unifields.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ydm1665702627365__topic_d53762e1_d53763e1_d53764e1_d53765e1_d53766e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d820828e84\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ydm1665702627365__p_d81545e1_d81546e1_d81547e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curline</span> function enables you to refer to particular lines of a field.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ydm1665702627365__section_cgm_thh_xbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d820828e97\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curline</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curline</span> to provide\n            context-sensitive help. The user positions the cursor on a particular line in the field\n            and activates the help trigger for that line:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ydm1665702627365__pre_fpq_5hh_xbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger help\n help $text(\"%%$curline%%%_HLP\")\nend; help</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/grv1719592389957.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$curword</a><p>Return the word on which the cursor is positioned in the current Unifield.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7424488\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7424488\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$curline Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 30, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $curline Return the line on which the cursor is positioned in the current Unifield. $curline Return Values Line number where the cursor is currently positioned in the Uniface field editor. Use Use in Form components, but only applicable to Unifields. Description The $curline function enables you to refer to particular lines of a field. Example: Using $curline The following example uses $curline to provide context-sensitive help. The user positions the cursor on a particular line in the field and activates the help trigger for that line: trigger help help $text(\"%%$curline%%%_HLP\") end; help Copy Related Links $curword Return the word on which the cursor is positioned in the current Unifield. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}